為何如此？<br />\n<br />\n想那日初次約會，心驚、手震、膽顫，忙裏洩露各種的醜態像喪屍。而尷尬是快餐廳裏，我誤把醬汁四周亂濺，駭人場面相當諷刺。<br />\n<br />\n你及時遞上餐紙，去為我清洗襯衣，剎那間身體的觸碰大件事！<br />\n<br />\n今天看這段歷史，像褪色午夜殘片。笑話情節此刻變窩心故事。現時大了，那種心跳難重演，極燦爛時光一去難再遇上一次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a588b71ad0171f320affaac60d48da649e73669","tid":951353,"uid":135281,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c40e335276aadff4c1ab90f4acc343a12b38a93","tid":951353,"uid":12421,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"雨に歌えば 雲は割れるか 賑やかな夏の干涸びた命だ<br />\n<br />\n拝啓 忌まわしき過去に告ぐ 絶縁の詩<br />\n最低な日々の 最悪な夢の 残骸を捨てては行けず ここで息絶えようと<br />\n後世 花は咲き君に伝う 変遷の詩<br />\n苦悩にまみれて 嘆き悲しみ それでも途絶えぬ歌に 陽は射さずとも"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecad50bb9721810d9d809afb7a3a62b6b3fc8cc","tid":951353,"uid":204124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:41:16.000Z","msg":"考DSE<br />\n<br />\n小伙子 長大了"},{"pid":"d878853765dc245fda6939413c2e33d1d1a31e68","tid":951353,"uid":43647,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"緩緩飄落的楓葉像思念<br />\n我點燃燭火溫暖歲末的秋天<br />\n利申：以前作文真係用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0798a8503ab5159e5992185e84f926caa86c0558","tid":951353,"uid":204024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"不來也原去全首<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如煙 因給你遞過火<br />\n如火 卻也沒熔掉我<br />\n回望最初 當喪失是得著可不可<br />\n可痛若驪歌 樂如兒歌<br />\n像你沒來過 沒去過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c19a867e49483a294a9bb233c30965a5e297a0d","tid":951353,"uid":204024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0798a8503ab5159e5992185e84f926caa86c0558","tid":951353,"uid":204024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"不來也原去全首<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如煙 因給你遞過火<br />\n如火 卻也沒熔掉我<br />\n回望最初 當喪失是得著可不可<br />\n可痛若驪歌 樂如兒歌<br />\n像你沒來過 沒去過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"不來也不去"},{"pid":"c512d11c8f64e990ca1c82b9a6ef7c3e0fd717d1","tid":951353,"uid":106336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dcda4b5cf3227ffcc3a65ef61dce8d2774aeca6","tid":951353,"uid":79382,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"喬遷那日，打掃廢物，家居彷似開戰，無意發現當天穿返學夏季襯衣。奇怪卻是，茄汁污垢滲在這襯衣布章外邊，極其大意，為何如此？<br />\n<br />\n想那日初次約會，心驚、手震、膽顫，忙裏洩露各種的醜態像喪屍。而尷尬是快餐廳裏，我誤把醬汁四周亂濺，駭人場面相當諷刺。<br />\n<br />\n你及時遞上餐紙，去為我清洗襯衣，剎那間身體的觸碰大件事！<br />\n<br />\n今天看這段歷史，像褪色午夜殘片。笑話情節此刻變窩心故事。現時大了，那種心跳難重演，極燦爛時光一去難再遇上一次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:17:46.000Z","msg":"淨係呢首歌都可以寫返一篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b45c99f29102c9443fdae207f896ba4f13e065f","tid":951353,"uid":135281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c512d11c8f64e990ca1c82b9a6ef7c3e0fd717d1","ti